Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:01:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把能替我保护你的人 我信任的朋友带来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色战士 登场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}ガンバレッド是一款很老的射击游戏，1994年出版
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸の奥が高鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い声に気づいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スタートラインは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:55.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素敵だと思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:00.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも不安はすぐ傍で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:06.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駆け出す思いを　締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を越えて　歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.46,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初めてを　繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.01,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掴み取れ　明日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうさ友達が無限の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:23.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢抱きしめ　進むのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:29.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝いてる自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる力に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大の愛をこめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うまま　変えた今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:44.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界乗り変え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开歌喉 高声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能注意到自己热情的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的起跑线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然前边的路看不到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的朝前走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:55.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:00.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不安一直徘徊在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:06.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就将自己这份雀跃的心情小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迈出自己的脚步 超越现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮前方那条未知的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成一个又一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的双手紧紧抓住未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们快来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:23.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起拥抱无限的梦想 朝前进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:29.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信闪闪发亮的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振奋人心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饱含着满满的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 改变今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:44.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起拥抱新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候完全无路可走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是现在 要释放这种力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}祝贺夺冠！白浜坂高中 田中大智
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:16.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなの希望が詰まったこの剣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.63,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,エターナルゾーンホリーブレード
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:27.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気丈を　涙を力に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:33.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　巨大な敵に立ち向かうのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:41.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever!(Forever!)(Forever!)Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:16.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝聚大家希望的这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.63,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是永恒的圣洁之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:27.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将勇气和眼泪化成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:34.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作气 挥刀冲向强大的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国大赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直想象着今天的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也想登上大舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 赛马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛马？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为骑手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和全力奔跑的马一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越所有人 快速冲向终点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～很帅气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们不要太闹腾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到庆祝的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是第一轮比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要抱着必胜的信念去参赛啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想要浪费维也纳的心血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这莫名其妙的想法算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 和奏的响葫芦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:32.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　巨大な敵に立ち向かうのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:32.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作气 挥刀冲向强大的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天身体不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:54.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad3\4c&HA6A4A5&\bord0\fad(400,200)}第五集  {\bord2\4c&HA1D734&} {\4c&HD7EEA6&\3c&HFBFEF0&\c&H8473F7&}时而舍弃 {\c&HE3A37C&\4c&H8973F9&}时而不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们太闹腾了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来夏是节日积极分子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节日？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中当初为神马开始打羽毛球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别省略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}纱羽把badminton（羽毛球）省略成badmin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请白滨坂高中的田中大智同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到指定场地候场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振奋精神 大干一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大智 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}是江户时代为了鼓动民众团结一致而喊的口号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用誓死的决心喊出口号 再在杯子里盛上营养丰富的饮料…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有粉红色的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉红色…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色不也很好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能帮我倒杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我做晚饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请在这边付钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜者和田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打进八强的话 已经相当厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打进四强的话就可以参加全国大赛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顺便买瓶绿茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿一下包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做想象练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在记忆还没被冲淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中是什么时候开始打羽毛球的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是小学三年级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始参加社团活动之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大智马上说也要参加 还想要自己的球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小学就开始打的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去羽毛球盛行的高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且念白高的话能骑自行车上学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前部里也有不少成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有我曾崇拜过的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是毕业于我们高中 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是因为这个选手 你才开始打羽毛球的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别省略了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是为了在夏天也不让身体冷却才卖热的绿茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 纱羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近好像没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 水好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是纱羽的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我志保
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没玩这个 身手迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对纱羽保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定会马上说 你已经不年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年比一年啰嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随便找个地方放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流汗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去冲个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是白高的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小和奏的学姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候说到这一带不是白中就是镰中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是小和奏的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真昼学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}祝贺合唱部夺得桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我大一岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是高仓学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓直子现在是教导主任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把这个好好重洗一张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家以前都是合唱部的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在比赛中夺冠后拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有听妈妈说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没跟她说过生病的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你瞧那孩子不是正在考试嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 接下来我会处理的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我来做今天的晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 当心点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你病倒了 吓我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也很快就能出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去借块抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 你要多加注意自己的身体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和你一起创作歌曲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会好起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多听听和奏的想法和意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我没闲工夫做这些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起来唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神太紧张的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是考不出好水平的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这都要怪谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹你生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一起创作歌曲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就会好起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 认真教我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不是示例嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小时候经常和我一起唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学习也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考试结束后也要继续学音乐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让音乐一直常伴在和奏左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不要忘却热爱音乐的情怀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试不过关的话就没有意义了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪到腰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那周六周日就你先顶着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边从周一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 这种事情是要互相关照的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野叔叔打来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说是又闪到腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算下周一去帮他做做农活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英彦先生又是上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不能突然请假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要去个两三天 没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭干脆叫寿司来吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把屋子里的钢琴处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能让给其他真心喜欢音乐的人用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妈妈也会欣慰的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留个小CD机就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再整理一下其他不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腾出来的位置就放张床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我明天就打电话问问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天从早上开始多云
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在强烈的低气压正向小笠原的近海处靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中午到傍晚将会有暴风雨天气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 补习拖到很晚的话 最好带上雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风力好像也会加强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会有人来把钢琴和其他东西的都拉走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我都标注清楚了 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 金鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲸鱼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金鱼啦 金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼啦 鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就取中间 当它是海豚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豚会唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我三点半也要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔家的手机虽然很难打通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但远野的号码你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭叫寿司外卖也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的话你也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要开派对庆祝大智进入前八强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想在下雨之前去买点东西就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在要搞羽毛球比赛的庆功宴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 今天有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蛋糕已经买了和奏的份了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有好大的草莓的那种哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少吃了蛋糕再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然很没精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是讨厌草莓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说她嫌我很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是稍微有点可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(伙食费)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小～虎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是让你把我的雨衣拿出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的东西自己准备好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带好准考证了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有忘带什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 别忘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西没啥用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都淋湿了 快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的人生之路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和我的女儿和奏一起携手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管健康亦或疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管快乐亦或悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得只要与和奏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能创作出那样的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对于我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲就是传递爱的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和奏教给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将想要传达给和奏的思念化作歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是能和她一起歌唱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还能听到和奏创作的歌曲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生就完美无缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连「我出门了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连「谢谢」也没有说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能一起唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:14.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴れた日雨の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:21.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんながいれば何時も笑顔になれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶の彼方まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:34.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出したりたゆたう声耳に澄まそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:40.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ　手を差し伸べられて輪の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:49.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人じゃない空間で夢中になってる 時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:54.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地よい風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:02.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑ったり泣いたり　歌ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉じていたココロを開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:14.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出のフレーズ　口ずさむ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:20.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏でよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:14.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天晴或者下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:21.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家在一起 随时都能展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:27.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往记忆的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:34.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆往事 倾听回荡在耳边的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:40.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 到伸手牵成的圆圈里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:49.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在大家的世界里 一起度过这梦幻般的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:54.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎面吹拂着清凉的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:02.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们笑过 哭过 放声高唱过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扬起心灵的风帆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:14.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱出回忆满满的歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:20.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起放声高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 你觉得我们最需要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 和奏 你待会儿有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}第六集 时而微笑 时而想念
